Link to Tech Updates on this page
With Font Awesome 7, we've made huge improvements to how icons work behind the scenes. From minor tweaks to major overhauls, our toolkit is now faster than ever.
Refined SVG/JS, optimized font files, and compressed CSS.
Upgraded to Dart Sass with modern SCSS and improved CSS properties.
Icon canvases now render at a fixed width, with new "automatic" option.
Better screen reader support, assistive tech, and RTL compatibility.
